{"tid":1668852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足，可唔可以唔好再搞交通燈？","createTime":"2019-10-22T08:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:51:31.000Z","uid":305644,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f82a8ac4619d3ea9624c897ce4cf7f47db27704","tid":1668852,"uid":305644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:25:00.000Z","msg":"講明先，唔係割，係檢討<br />\n<br />\n其實交通燈真係好平架炸，一部只不過萬五蚊左右，仲平過黨鐵d閘機，當你打爆200舊交通燈，都只不過係300萬左右，但係打個時又辛苦，打完又基本上唔係食到政府好多維修費，之後受影響得最多既又只係普通市民，咁有咩用呢？<br />\n雖然話民意唔會再大逆轉，但係成日係街都聽到有人鬧手足，真係唔好受。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得萬五蚊好多，不如試下打d冇咩用既交通燈，姐係過馬路個時係安全島個到個d燈，真係唔好打爆哂全部。<br />\n<br />\n[交通燈價錢來源：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/58500/%E5%85%AC%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%95%E5%83%B9-%E6%92%9E%E6%AF%80%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E5%90%84%E5%8D%80%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C-%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%A040%E8%90%AC]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F58500%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%2589%25A9%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2583%25B9-%25E6%2592%259E%25E6%25AF%2580%25E9%2581%2593%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%2590%2584%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%2584%259F%25E5%2583%25B9%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%259B%25BE%25E8%25B3%25A040%25E8%2590%25AC%5D&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=294248d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/58500/%E5%85%AC%E7%89%A9%E4%BD%95%E5%83%B9-%E6%92%9E%E6%AF%80%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF%E8%A8%AD%E6%96%BD%E5%90%84%E5%8D%80%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C-%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E6%9B%BE%E8%B3%A040%E8%90%AC]</a>"},{"pid":"464d87e424fbb1ab63b2f61707a400d53bdebd5d","tid":1668852,"uid":285261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"請問有乜野可以搞？<br />\n駕駛人士話中仲方便左"},{"pid":"a81779a518d991dc054214171a1296